column5: Bill, nice fish... thanks for sharing
Bill: I thought for sure the caption for that first pic was going to be -----"Largest walleye of the trip".........................
That is the smallest walleye I have ever caught in 50 plus years of walleye fishing.Bill
my son caught a 5 1/2" walleye in mid august at steamboat. i got a 4 1/2" perch. i had the previous record for walleye at 7 1/2". no more.
